{"tid":2336524,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有兩日就到聖誕","createTime":"2020-12-22T16:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T16:29:45.000Z","uid":370062,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7f49e95574223c48d4c694668a83809871b30ddc","tid":2336524,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T16:02:59.000Z","msg":"希望各位連登巴絲可以開開心心過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論親情友情定愛情都可以一直保持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聖誕當日約咗屋企人朋友另一半嘅玩得開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未約嘅希望你哋快啲約到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溝緊仔或女嘅希望你哋快啲溝到然後甜甜蜜蜜過聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總之希望大家今年過個開心愉快幸福嘅聖誕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好好似本行咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ccdafac1525f4da34fc2ab115033cc8ad3e89a","tid":2336524,"uid":376618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T16:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc6f916964fd78d208caa5efc4ba4618291c65f","tid":2336524,"uid":370062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"67ccdafac1525f4da34fc2ab115033cc8ad3e89a","tid":2336524,"uid":376618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T16:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T16:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聖誕快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"